\"color: rgb(68,68,68); text-decoration: none\"></a>\r\n<p class=\"pic-info\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.5; padding-right: 0px\"><a title=\"查看图片\" href=\"http://detail.1688.com/offer/1260121435.html#\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(68,68,68); text-decoration: none\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: medium\">收银纸，顾名思义，它是指收银机里使用的记录收银明细的纸卷，主要用于向顾客提供购物明细清单，用完后可更换。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-align: left; font: 12px Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\">一般收银纸的材质为适用于收银机内部打印部件的相应材质。对普通针式打印机来讲，可以使用普通1-3层打印纸来打印；对热敏头式打印机来讲，只能使用热敏打印纸来打印。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-align: left; font: 12px Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\">普通针式打印机，需使用色带及收银纸等打印耗材。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-align: left; font: 12px Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\">热敏头式打印机，只有需使用热敏打印纸即可以进行打印，不需其它辅助耗材。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-align: left; font: 12px Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span class=\"headline-content\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\">收银纸分四大类</span></span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-align: left; font: 12px Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\">1、双胶纸：使用普通双胶纸加工生产的收银纸，全部是单层的，纸面上没有任何涂层，靠色带在上面打印出字的收银纸。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-align: left; font: 12px Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\">2、热敏纸：使用热敏纸加工生产的收银纸，全部是单层的，纸面上涂有热敏化学涂层，纸张经激光热敏头打印显色的收银纸，其特点是不用打印耗材，不用碳带、色带或墨盒；而且纸张表面比较光滑，用指甲或硬物在纸张上划过时会有清楚的印迹。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-align: left; font: 12px Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\">3、无碳纸：这种收银纸最少由两层或以上构成，其中第一联需用针式打印机来打印显色，但后面的几联靠针式打印机打印压力显色。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-align: left; font: 12px Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\">4、自感纸：这种收银纸由一层或多层构成，靠针式打印机打印压力显色，打印纸不需要安装色带。这种收银纸的第一联叫自感纸，后面的几联即是普通无碳纸。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-align: left; font: 12px Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span class=\"headline-content\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\">常用收银纸型号</span></span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-align: left; font: 12px Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\">常见收银纸主要有热敏纸、普通双胶纸及无碳纸三种</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-align: left; font: 12px Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\">热敏的一般常用规格有</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-align: left; font: 12px Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\">57x50型、57x60型、57&times;80型、75x50型、75x60型、75x80型、80x50型、80x60型、80x80，80&times;140型等</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51,51,51); text-align: left; font: 12px Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\">普通双胶纸常用规格有</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transf