"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">●静电吸附技术，不含胶水可多次粘贴；●滤光增艳，画质亮丽出彩，感观享受；<br />\r\n●高硬华处理，持久抗刮；&nbsp;●PET材质制成，质地轻薄，透光度好，清晰体验；&nbsp;<br />\r\n●过滤90%紫外线，低反射，视域广阔；●防指纹防油污，有需要时可水洗重复使用；</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">[功能特性]:</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">●&nbsp;&nbsp; 高清无尘</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 采用以透明聚脂薄膜为主要成分的日本原装PET材质,日本全机械无尘工序生产,高透明度且不会产生细小杂点,保护贴达到光学级的透明度,保证屏幕的完美清晰度.</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">●&nbsp;&nbsp; 抗指纹、防刮<br />\r\n&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 保护贴的表层经过特殊的抗静电处理,表面可以有效的避免指纹残留、笔迹墨水或空气中的灰尘沾附于其上.表面经过独有的HC处理达3H硬度,耐磨抗刮花.</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">●&nbsp;&nbsp; 适应环境<br />\r\n&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 低温零下10度,高温80度,即使面对恶劣的环境永不脱落.</font><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">●&nbsp;&nbsp; 防辐射、除电磁波<br />\r\n&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 隔绝电磁波99.7﹪以上的磁场辐射,减低辐射源污染,更舒适健康.</font><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">●&nbsp;&nbsp; 超高透光率<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 97﹪超高透光率,独有透光处理技术,增加液晶显示屏的色彩还原度,让画面更靓丽,更清晰.</font><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">●&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;静电吸附，无痕无胶&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 通过静电吸附的保护贴，从机身上撕下来之后不会留有微痕，不会破坏光洁无暇的表面，无残胶，持久长效，可以无限替换，安全保护。</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">一、&nbsp;产品特征:<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.&nbsp;产品采用原种日本进口PET材料,属于新一代高透型三层液晶屏幕保护专用材料；</font><font face=\"Verdana\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.&nbsp;保护膜表面经耐磨防刮花处理，耐磨强度为4H；<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3.&nbsp;保护膜防经紫外线处理,避免紫外线对液晶屏的伤害;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.&nbsp;可减少反光达90%,透光率达99%,粘贴后使屏幕更加清晰逼真；<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.&nbsp;完全采用静电吸附原理，使粘贴更简捷，不易产生气泡;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6.&nbsp;独特的微圆角设计，更贴近屏幕边缘；<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 7.&nbsp;多种规格匹配各种尺寸笔记本电脑屏幕。</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#ff0000\"><font color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\" face=\"Verdana\">二、&nbsp;功能特性：<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.&nbsp;有效防止笔记本电脑屏幕的划伤及磨损；<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.&nbsp;表面抗静电,不易聚积灰尘，防污型强，可用软布擦拭；<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3.&nbsp;直接接触不易留下指纹；<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.&nbsp;有特殊防反射,眩光功能,消除98%的环境反射光，并具一定的防偷窥性；<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.&nbsp;超高透性，明亮如镜。</font></font></font></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font color=\"#0033ff\" size=\"4\" face=\"宋体\">隔离灰尘--有效增强色彩，视觉效果更加清晰。<br />\r\n静电吸附--静电离子吸附，绝无残胶不伤屏幕。<br />\r\n超高透光--进口特种材质，视觉近乎隐形效果。</font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><font style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font size=\"6\"><strong><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/373782179/T239BPXwBaXXXXXXXX_!!373782179.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" /></strong></font></font></font></font></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"5\">实物演练：</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><font style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"6\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><img align=\"absMiddle\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/231718107/T2P3jXXXJXXXXXXXXX_!!231718107.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" /></font></font></font></font></font></span></span></span></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; list-style: none; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">\r\n    <li align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal outside;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#ff0000\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">先清洁要贴的本本屏幕,</span><span style=\"color: black;\">一定要清洁干净,</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">否则留有灰尘会有出现小气泡的。</span></font><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><br />\r\n    <font color=\"#3366cc\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\"><img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/a11c9869714yg193f50c3855ddda27cad30ca5636.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" alt=\"\" /></span></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></li>\r\n    <li align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal outside;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><font color=\"#3366cc\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">小贴示</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">:</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">清洁剂尽量喷在布上</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">虽然喷在屏上也没有影响</span></font></font><font color=\"#3366cc\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">.</span></font></font><br />\r\n    <font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366cc\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">首先拿出<a href=\"http://shop.mall.taobao.com/search-52006-0----1-grid-1845.htm\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\"><font color=\"#3366cc\" size=\"2\" face=\"Arial\">屏幕贴膜</font></a>看看</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">尺寸和屏幕是否一致</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">.</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">确认好后</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">您会看到保护膜上有标有</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">和</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">的小贴纸</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">先把标有</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">的贴纸如下图折一下</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">.</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></font></font><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\"><br />\r\n    <img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/4586eb36e697t14143f3ad3a9a8fecfd3e4d337a8.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" alt=\"\" /></span></font></font></font></font></font></font></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">再把屏贴反过来</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">把标有</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">的贴纸朝下</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">这面是贴到屏幕上去的</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">先揭一点就可以了</span></font></font><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\"><font color=\"#3366ff\" size=\"3\">.<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/4016bl97141620bc1efadc982a7d01577b85d8f13.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" /></font></span></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; list-style: none; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">\r\n    <li align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal outside;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\">开始贴了看下图,沿着一边,尽量使膜的一边和本本屏幕外壳平行.慢慢放下去.因为贴膜有静电吸附能力,所以会自动吸附到屏上.</font></font></font></font></font></font></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/b70eece6971l417e502cfebbe0ca3b28e7d5c9186.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" /></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/74aeb06e9b714137fb99c116bb5840bd01f0ee086.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" /></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0pt 39pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: -18pt; word-break: break-all;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\';\">:</span></font><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\">第一,会发现贴膜上吸附一些小灰尘.贴上去会有气泡</font></font><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\">.<br />\r\n解决方法:用之前准备好的胶带纸,如下图,找到有小灰尘的地方,用胶带把灰尘粘掉就可以了</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/63bedfc69714jd18149d2a57a9bef1394b1c5d2c7.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" /></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0pt 39pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: -18pt; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; list-style: none; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal outside;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\">第二,出现小气泡,先把贴膜稍揭回去,放掉气泡再贴回去.如果还不行,可以用魔布,慢慢擦过去应该可以搞定。</font></font></font></font><br />\r\n    <font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\">继续耐心的贴<font face=\"Tahoma\">,</font>边贴边处理小气泡<font face=\"Tahoma\">,</font>直到全部贴好<font face=\"Tahoma\">.</font>注意最后收尾的时候收到一个角上去就可以了<font face=\"Tahoma\">.</font>然后撕开标有<font face=\"Tahoma\">2</font>的标签</font></font><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\" face=\"Tahoma\">.&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></font></font></font></font></font></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;<font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/6cd3cfr69714u15367c61ae064b18058b5cf675a6.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" /></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><span style=\"font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><font color=\"#3366ff\" size=\"3\">贴完有可能还会残留一些小气泡,一般情况下一周左右会自己消失,请放心。</font></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\"><font color=\"#3366ff\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/32d96a9f7141d8db46e506a42b33ee2634b349c84.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></span></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0pt 39pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: -18pt; word-break: break-all;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\"><font color=\"#3366ff\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 完事了,这是亮丽屏贴,效果很眩吧~</font></span></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\"><strong><font size=\"4\">[功效]：<br />\r\n1、保护液晶<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;亮丽贴表面硬度大于一般液晶表面偏光膜，且光滑，可有效抵御意外划伤和磨损。</font><font size=\"4\">2、镜面效果液晶亮丽贴，能够把普通液晶屏，变成具有镜面效果的贵丽屏！</font><font size=\"4\">3、增亮<br />\r\n普通屏的磨砂表面，使灯管光在穿出液晶表面的时候，被大量散射，进入人眼的光线减少。但贴了亮丽贴后，灯管发出的光亮，几乎完全垂直射出，更多进入人眼，当然能提高屏幕明亮程度！</font></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\"><strong><font color=\"#0033ff\" size=\"4\" face=\"宋体\">隔离灰尘--有效增强色彩，视觉效果更加清晰。<br />\r\n静电吸附--静电离子吸附，绝无残胶不伤屏幕。<br />\r\n超高透光--进口特种材质，视觉近乎隐形效果。</font></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><font color=\"#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 10pt;\">&lt;1&gt;<font size=\"3\">贴膜之前先比较一下尺寸是否合适，如果稍小，贴膜可以居中贴.</font></span></font></span></span><font color=\"#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 10pt;\"><font size=\"3\">清洁屏幕表面，这一步最重要，灰尘和毛毛要彻底清除干净，否则贴膜时会出现气泡；</font></span></font><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 10pt;\"><font color=\"#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&lt;2&gt;<font size=\"3\">标签朝下，撕开有标签的一层/<font color=\"#ff0000\">标有⑴的那面</font>（此层是保护层，揭掉不要的），</font></span></font></span></font><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 10pt;\"><font color=\"#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><font size=\"3\">对齐屏幕一端，开始贴膜，如果贴的过程中发现歪了，可以揭起来重新粘贴；</font></span></font></span></font><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 10pt;\"><font color=\"#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><font size=\"3\">一手慢慢拉开带标签的保护层，另一手用硬卡刮除气泡。<font color=\"#ff0000\">贴好后，除去标有⑵的那层。</font></font></span></font></span></font><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 10pt;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-size: 10pt;\"><font color=\"#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&lt;3&gt;<font size=\"3\">贴膜完成。如果还有小许气泡。不用担心，不用去理会，可放心使用/一般过一个星期气泡会慢慢少去<font color=\"#ff0000\">。</font></font></span></font></span></font></span></font></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\"><strong><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 10pt;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"3\">（开机使用，屏幕会发热，久之气泡就会分散直至消失）</font></span></font></strong></span></span></span></span></p>','images/201401/thumb_img/6473_thumb_G_1389497087380.jpg','images/201401/goods_img/6473_G_1389497087746.jpg','images/201401/source_img/6473_G_1389497087323.png','1','','1','1','0','0','1389497087','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1389497362','0','','0','0','0','0');
INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('6474','984','0','ECS006474','笔记本静电膜15.6”（10个起批）','+','151','0','','80','0.000','0.00','2.70','0.00','0','0','1','','','<p>&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-family: 黑体; color: rgb(0, 102, 51); font-size: medium; line-height: 21px;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"7\">屏幕膜</font></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><font style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"6\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#006633\" size=\"3\" face=\"宋体\"><font face=\"黑体\">采用 &quot;静电离子吸附&quot; 技术，保护屏幕隔离灰尘、让液晶屏幕长久如新,使安装更为简便，视觉效果更加舒适，完全避免残胶问题，去除时不损伤液晶屏幕，更有效防护液晶屏幕。</font><br />\r\n《</font><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#006633\" face=\"宋体\">抗刮强化》镜面抗刮处理，真正有效防护液晶。</font></font></font></font></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><font style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"6\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#006633\" face=\"宋体\">《隔离反光》有效消除炫光，视觉效果更加清晰。</font></font></font></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><font style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"6\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\">《静电吸附》静电离子吸附，绝无残胶不伤屏幕。</font><font size=\"3\">《超高透光》进口材质，视觉近乎隐形效果</font></font></font></font></font></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">●静电吸附技术，不含胶水可多次粘贴；●滤光增艳，画质亮丽出彩，感观享受；<br />\r\n●高硬华处理，持久抗刮；&nbsp;●PET材质制成，质地轻薄，透光度好，清晰体验；&nbsp;<br />\r\n●过滤90%紫外线，低反射，视域广阔；●防指纹防油污，有需要时可水洗重复使用；</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">[功能特性]:</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">●&nbsp;&nbsp; 高清无尘</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 采用以透明聚脂薄膜为主要成分的日本原装PET材质,日本全机械无尘工序生产,高透明度且不会产生细小杂点,保护贴达到光学级的透明度,保证屏幕的完美清晰度.</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">●&nbsp;&nbsp; 抗指纹、防刮<br />\r\n&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 保护贴的表层经过特殊的抗静电处理,表面可以有效的避免指纹残留、笔迹墨水或空气中的灰尘沾附于其上.表面经过独有的HC处理达3H硬度,耐磨抗刮花.</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">●&nbsp;&nbsp; 适应环境<br />\r\n&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 低温零下10度,高温80度,即使面对恶劣的环境永不脱落.</font><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">●&nbsp;&nbsp; 防辐射、除电磁波<br />\r\n&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 隔绝电磁波99.7﹪以上的磁场辐射,减低辐射源污染,更舒适健康.</font><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">●&nbsp;&nbsp; 超高透光率<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 97﹪超高透光率,独有透光处理技术,增加液晶显示屏的色彩还原度,让画面更靓丽,更清晰.</font><font color=\"#1111ee\" size=\"3\">●&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;静电吸附，无痕无胶&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 通过静电吸附的保护贴，从机身上撕下来之后不会留有微痕，不会破坏光洁无暇的表面，无残胶，持久长效，可以无限替换，安全保护。</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">一、&nbsp;产品特征:<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.&nbsp;产品采用原种日本进口PET材料,属于新一代高透型三层液晶屏幕保护专用材料；</font><font face=\"Verdana\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.&nbsp;保护膜表面经耐磨防刮花处理，耐磨强度为4H；<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3.&nbsp;保护膜防经紫外线处理,避免紫外线对液晶屏的伤害;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.&nbsp;可减少反光达90%,透光率达99%,粘贴后使屏幕更加清晰逼真；<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.&nbsp;完全采用静电吸附原理，使粘贴更简捷，不易产生气泡;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6.&nbsp;独特的微圆角设计，更贴近屏幕边缘；<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 7.&nbsp;多种规格匹配各种尺寸笔记本电脑屏幕。</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#ff0000\"><font color=\"#000000\" size=\"4\" face=\"Verdana\">二、&nbsp;功能特性：<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.&nbsp;有效防止笔记本电脑屏幕的划伤及磨损；<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.&nbsp;表面抗静电,不易聚积灰尘，防污型强，可用软布擦拭；<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3.&nbsp;直接接触不易留下指纹；<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.&nbsp;有特殊防反射,眩光功能,消除98%的环境反射光，并具一定的防偷窥性；<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.&nbsp;超高透性，明亮如镜。</font></font></font></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font color=\"#0033ff\" size=\"4\" face=\"宋体\">隔离灰尘--有效增强色彩，视觉效果更加清晰。<br />\r\n静电吸附--静电离子吸附，绝无残胶不伤屏幕。<br />\r\n超高透光--进口特种材质，视觉近乎隐形效果。</font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><font style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font size=\"6\"><strong><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/373782179/T239BPXwBaXXXXXXXX_!!373782179.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" /></strong></font></font></font></font></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"5\">实物演练：</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><font style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"6\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><img align=\"absMiddle\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/231718107/T2P3jXXXJXXXXXXXXX_!!231718107.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" /></font></font></font></font></font></span></span></span></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; list-style: none; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">\r\n    <li align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal outside;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#ff0000\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">先清洁要贴的本本屏幕,</span><span style=\"color: black;\">一定要清洁干净,</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">否则留有灰尘会有出现小气泡的。</span></font><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><br />\r\n    <font color=\"#3366cc\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\"><img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/a11c9869714yg193f50c3855ddda27cad30ca5636.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" alt=\"\" /></span></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></li>\r\n    <li align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal outside;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><font color=\"#3366cc\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">小贴示</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">:</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">清洁剂尽量喷在布上</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">虽然喷在屏上也没有影响</span></font></font><font color=\"#3366cc\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">.</span></font></font><br />\r\n    <font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366cc\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">首先拿出<a href=\"http://shop.mall.taobao.com/search-52006-0----1-grid-1845.htm\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\"><font color=\"#3366cc\" size=\"2\" face=\"Arial\">屏幕贴膜</font></a>看看</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">尺寸和屏幕是否一致</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">.</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">确认好后</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">您会看到保护膜上有标有</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">和</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">的小贴纸</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">先把标有</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">的贴纸如下图折一下</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">.</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></font></font><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\"><br />\r\n    <img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/4586eb36e697t14143f3ad3a9a8fecfd3e4d337a8.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" alt=\"\" /></span></font></font></font></font></font></font></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">再把屏贴反过来</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">把标有</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">的贴纸朝下</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">这面是贴到屏幕上去的</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\">,</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; color: black;\">先揭一点就可以了</span></font></font><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\"><font color=\"#3366ff\" size=\"3\">.<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/4016bl97141620bc1efadc982a7d01577b85d8f13.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" /></font></span></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; list-style: none; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">\r\n    <li align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal outside;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\">开始贴了看下图,沿着一边,尽量使膜的一边和本本屏幕外壳平行.慢慢放下去.因为贴膜有静电吸附能力,所以会自动吸附到屏上.</font></font></font></font></font></font></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/b70eece6971l417e502cfebbe0ca3b28e7d5c9186.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" /></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/74aeb06e9b714137fb99c116bb5840bd01f0ee086.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" /></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0pt 39pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: -18pt; word-break: break-all;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\';\">:</span></font><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\">第一,会发现贴膜上吸附一些小灰尘.贴上去会有气泡</font></font><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\">.<br />\r\n解决方法:用之前准备好的胶带纸,如下图,找到有小灰尘的地方,用胶带把灰尘粘掉就可以了</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/63bedfc69714jd18149d2a57a9bef1394b1c5d2c7.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" /></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0pt 39pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: -18pt; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; list-style: none; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: decimal outside;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\">第二,出现小气泡,先把贴膜稍揭回去,放掉气泡再贴回去.如果还不行,可以用魔布,慢慢擦过去应该可以搞定。</font></font></font></font><br />\r\n    <font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\">继续耐心的贴<font face=\"Tahoma\">,</font>边贴边处理小气泡<font face=\"Tahoma\">,</font>直到全部贴好<font face=\"Tahoma\">.</font>注意最后收尾的时候收到一个角上去就可以了<font face=\"Tahoma\">.</font>然后撕开标有<font face=\"Tahoma\">2</font>的标签</font></font><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\" face=\"Tahoma\">.&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></font></font></font></font></font></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;<font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/6cd3cfr69714u15367c61ae064b18058b5cf675a6.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" /></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><span style=\"font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><font color=\"#3366ff\" size=\"3\">贴完有可能还会残留一些小气泡,一般情况下一周左右会自己消失,请放心。</font></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\"><font color=\"#3366ff\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"http://img.isso.com.cn/upload_2010/day_101219/32d96a9f7141d8db46e506a42b33ee2634b349c84.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></span></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0pt 39pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: -18pt; word-break: break-all;\"><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#006633\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"3\"><font color=\"#3366ff\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: \'tahoma sans-serif\'; color: black;\"><font color=\"#3366ff\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 完事了,这是亮丽屏贴,效果很眩吧~</font></span></font></font></font></font></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\"><strong><font size=\"4\">[功效]：<br />\r\n1、保护液晶<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;亮丽贴表面硬度大于一般液晶表面偏光膜，且光滑，可有效抵御意外划伤和磨损。</font><font size=\"4\">2、镜面效果液晶亮丽贴，能够把普通液晶屏，变成具有镜面效果的贵丽屏！</font><font size=\"4\">3、增亮<br />\r\n普通屏的磨砂表面，使灯管光在穿出液晶表面的时候，被大量散射，进入人眼的光线减少。但贴了亮丽贴后，灯管发出的光亮，几乎完全垂直射出，更多进入人眼，当然能提高屏幕明亮程度！</font></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\"><strong><font color=\"#0033ff\" size=\"4\" face=\"宋体\">隔离灰尘--有效增强色彩，视觉效果更加清晰。<br />\r\n静电吸附--静电离子吸附，绝无残胶不伤屏幕。<br />\r\n超高透光--进口特种材质，视觉近乎隐形效果。</font></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><font color=\"#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 10pt;\">&lt;1&gt;<font size=\"3\">贴膜之前先比较一下尺寸是否合适，如果稍小，贴膜可以居中贴.</font></span></font></span></span><font color=\"#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 10pt;\"><font size=\"3\">清洁屏幕表面，这一步最重要，灰尘和毛毛要彻底清除干净，否则贴膜时会出现气泡；</font></span></font><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 10pt;\"><font color=\"#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&lt;2&gt;<font size=\"3\">标签朝下，撕开有标签的一层/<font color=\"#ff0000\">标有⑴的那面</font>（此层是保护层，揭掉不要的），</font></span></font></span></font><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 10pt;\"><font color=\"#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><font size=\"3\">对齐屏幕一端，开始贴膜，如果贴的过程中发现歪了，可以揭起来重新粘贴；</font></span></font></span></font><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 10pt;\"><font color=\"#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><font size=\"3\">一手慢慢拉开带标签的保护层，另一手用硬卡刮除气泡。<font color=\"#ff0000\">贴好后，除去标有⑵的那层。</font></font></span></font></span></font><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 10pt;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-size: 10pt;\"><font color=\"#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&lt;3&gt;<font size=\"3\">贴膜完成。如果还有小许气泡。不用担心，不用去理会，可放心使用/一般过一个星期气泡会慢慢少去<font color=\"#ff0000\">。</font></font></span></font></span></font></span></font></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\"><strong><font color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 10pt;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"3\">（开机使用，屏幕会发热，久之气泡就会分散直至消失）</font></span></font></strong></span></span></span></span></p>','images/201401/thumb_img/6474_thumb_G_1389497130059.jpg','images/201401/goods_img/6474_G_1389497130287.jpg','images/201401/source_img/6474_G_1389497130184.png','1','','1','1','0','0','1389497130','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1389497373','0','','0','0','0','0');
