0px; padding-top: 0px\">内置2600mAh大容量锂电池，持久供电</h3>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">TL-MR10U内置2600mAh大容量锂电池，典型应用*下可使用7-8小时，持久的电力供应足以满足大多数用户的户外上网需求。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">*典型应用是指1个无线客户端正常浏览网页、收发邮件，观看在线视频等持续交替进行的典型上网行为</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); text-indent: 0px; margin: 19px 0px 6px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,102,255); font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">可作为移动电源给手机充电</h3>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">TL-MR10U提供1个标准USB接口， 可作为移动电源给手机充电。&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); text-indent: 0px; margin: 19px 0px 6px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,102,255); font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">提供3G 、Router、AP三种工作模式，使用更方便</h3>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">TL-MR10U提供3G、Router、AP 共三种工作模式，一般情况下，不同环境对应的工作模式推荐如下：</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">户外环境&mdash;&mdash;3G模式，轻松化3G为Wi-Fi，即插即用，无需配置（出厂默认为3G模式）</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">家庭环境&mdash;&mdash;Router模式，支持笔记本、手机、Pad等多台终端以无线方式接入共享网络带宽</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">酒店环境&mdash;&mdash;AP模式，即插即用，无需配置</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); text-indent: 0px; margin: 19px 0px 6px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,102,255); font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">支持3G接入，兼容主流3G上网卡</h3>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0