0px !important; background-position: 0px 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><br />\r\n<div id=\"product-social-button\" class=\"span4\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 24px; width: 280px; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<div id=\"ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ctl00_overview1_Product_Info1_div_ShareThis\" class=\"pull-right\" style=\"float: right;\"><a title=\"人人网\" class=\"addico add_22\" item=\"22\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 185, 255); padding-right: 20px;\">&nbsp;</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</aside><section id=\"sectionOverview\" style=\"width: 946px; margin: 0px auto; padding: 40px 0px 20px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span id=\"ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ctl00_overview1_span_overview\">\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<h3 class=\"down_5\" style=\"margin: 100px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px 15px 0px 0px;\">超越极限的极致之美</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">在数千年艺术遗产的启发下，全新的 VX229N展现优雅和精湛工艺的日晷型设计。VX229N采用178&deg;超广视角AH-IPS A +技术的无边框面板，提供令人惊艳的视觉效果。此外，VX229N采用极具魅力的超薄机身及人体工学设计确保用户获得绝佳的视觉效果。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center up_1\" alt=\"Superior Image Quality Meets Frameless Elegant Design\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/lXRt9e8OabMKSCkd/vx01.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-top: -20px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Superior Image Quality Meets Frameless Elegant Design\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/CN/products/TTFDkcUTt4ejVTOe/image004.jpg\" longdesc=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/Monitors_Projectors/VX229N/\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Superior Image Quality Meets Frameless Elegant Design\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/CN/products/TTFDkcUTt4ejVTOe/image005.jpg\" longdesc=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/Monitors_Projectors/VX229N/\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /><br />\r\n华硕VX系列显示器具有超薄的外型设计，VX229N最薄处仅14.5mm，从而大幅降低桌面空间的需求。此外，VX229N提供了一个边框厚度仅0.8 mm的无边框屏幕。这种精细而优雅的设计，因日晷型底座的风格而更加彰显，它为显示器提供了一个稳固的底座。VX系列的设计荣获了2012年Good Design Awards的设计大奖。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">丰富的连接性提供各种多媒体娱乐</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">VX229N采用丰富的连接性包括DVI-D接口和D-sub接口，让您尽情享受多媒体影音娱乐。</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 28px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">栩栩如生、令人惊艳的视觉享受</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">最新IPS技术及178&deg;超广视角</h3>\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img alt=\"Vivid, lifelike visuals \" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/lXRt9e8OabMKSCkd/vx05.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<p class=\"down_3\" style=\"margin: 60px 0px 4em;\">VX229N采用16:9 LED背光AH-IPS A+面板及178&deg;超广视角，以确保从最极端的角度观赏，将色彩偏移降至最小化。AH-IPS是最新的IPS技术&ndash;提供精准色彩且绿色能效。</p>\r\n<img class=\"up_1\" alt=\"Vivid, lifelike visuals\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/lXRt9e8OabMKSCkd/ips_wide.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-top: -20px; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">80,000,000:1 华硕智能动态对比度</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">采用 80,000,000:1 华硕智能对比度(ASCR)以及250cd/m&sup2;的亮度显示，藉由背光的亮度调整，令黑色更加深邃动人，亮色更加鲜明亮丽，细节表现更出众，画面内容更生动。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center\" alt=\"80,000,000:1 ASUS Smart Contrast Ratio\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/lXRt9e8OabMKSCkd/contrastRatio.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\"><img class=\"top left\" alt=\"ASUS-exclusive VividPixel Technology\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/lXRt9e8OabMKSCkd/vividPixel.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; float: left; margin: 0px 1.5em 1.5em 0px; max-width: none;\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">华硕独家VividPixel技术</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">VividPixel技术用来增强图像及视频的轮廓，锐度和色彩饱和度，提供高品质的视觉体验。</p>\r\n<br style=\"clear: both;\" />\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\"><img alt=\"Monitor without VividPixel\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/lXRt9e8OabMKSCkd/pixel_1.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">显示器没有搭配VividPixel技术</h4>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px 25px;\">\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">图像质量主要依赖于面板本身</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">如果原始图像质量不好，则会产生模糊。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">通常人们没有注意到这个细节，因为没有进行比较。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\"><img alt=\"Monitor without VividPixel\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/lXRt9e8OabMKSCkd/pixel_2.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">VX 系列- IPS面板搭配VividPixel技术</h4>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px 25px;\">\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">IPS面板带给您超凡视觉享受</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">VividPixel默认值为25，自动调校图像质量。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">在VividPixel设置中选择其中的5个选项来浏览更多的不同效果。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.asus.com/Display/Features/Splendid_Technology/\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-decoration: none;\"><img class=\"right top down_2\" title=\"Learn More on Splendid Technology\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/images/icons/LCD/splendid_with_srgb.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em 1.5em; float: right; max-width: none;\" /></a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">Splendid&trade;靓彩影像增强技术</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">智能靓彩技术通过对亮度、对比度、色彩的锐利度、饱和度以及色温、肤色色度等智能处理和调节，还可以通过热键来切换6种不同的情景模式（风景、剧院、游戏、夜间、sRGB和标准模式），使得色彩和图像质量表现的更完美和生动。</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_abbb\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">华硕独家QuickFit虚拟比例</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">VX229N配备华硕独家QuickFit虚拟比例功能，允许用户在屏幕上预览相片及文件打印前的实际尺寸。它可通过显示器上的热键启动，并以此为指南精准地预览及编辑照片。</p>\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 218.296875px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<ul class=\"blackcircle\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none outside none;\"><strong>支持格式:</strong>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 13px; background-image: url(http://www.asus.com.cn/images/blackcircle.gif); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 5px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">文件：A4, 信件</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 13px; background-image: url(http://www.asus.com.cn/images/blackcircle.gif); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 5px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">图片：8&rdquo;x10&rdquo;, 5&rdquo;x7&rdquo;, 4&rdquo;x6&rdquo;, 3&rdquo;x5&rdquo;, 2&rdquo;x2&rdquo;</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 13px; background-image: url(http://www.asus.com.cn/images/blackcircle.gif); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 5px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">坐标预览：实际尺寸、厘米与英寸</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 703.421875px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center up_1\" alt=\"QuickFit Virtual Scale\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/lXRt9e8OabMKSCkd/vitualScalet.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-top: -20px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</span></section></p>','