4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">华硕智能动态对比度可达 80,000,000:1</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">华硕智能动态对比技术将动态对比度提升至80,000,000:1，令黑色更加深邃动人，亮色更加鲜明亮丽，细节表现更出众，画面内容更生动。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img class=\"center\" title=\"50,000,000:1 ASUS Smart Contrast Ratio\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/M3CJAGJS9lMXRZ0i/07.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">支持全高清1080p</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">支持全高清1080p（1920*1080），带领您进入令人炫目的彩色世界。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img class=\"center\" title=\"Full HD with HDMI\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/M3CJAGJS9lMXRZ0i/06_noHDMI.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">画面比例控制功能</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\"><img class=\"right top\" title=\"4:3 Aspect Control\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/M3CJAGJS9lMXRZ0i/43.gif\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; float: right; margin: -20px 0px 1.5em 1.5em; max-width: none;\" />比例控制功能可让用户选择最理想的显示模式，包括全屏幕与 4:3，让您在享受游戏或观赏影片时，不会遗漏任何信息或产生影像变形的情形。</p>\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">丰富的连接性及内置立体声扬声器，尽享无限的娱乐盛宴！</h4>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">VX238T-W 提供了丰富的I/O接口，包括DVI-D 与D-sub，方便用户轻松连接到各种设备，享受无限的娱乐盛宴。内建隐藏式立体声扬声器，提升多媒体娱乐体验。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.asus.com/Display/Features/Splendid_Technology/\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-decoration: none;\"><img class=\"right top down_2\" title=\"Learn More on Splendid Technology\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/images/icons/LCD/splendid_with_srgb.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em 1.5em; float: right; max-width: none;\" /></a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">Splendid&trade; 智能靓彩技术</h4>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">Splendid&trade; 智能靓彩技术通过对亮度、对比度、色彩的锐利度、饱和度以及色温、肤色色度等智能处理和调节，还可以通过热键来切换六种预设场景模式(剧院，风景，夜间，游戏，sRGB 和标准) 针对不同的使用情景进行最佳化处理，使得色彩和图像质量表现的更完美和生动。</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">QuickFit虚拟尺标</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em;\"><img class=\"right top\" title=\"QuickFit Virtual Scale\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/M3CJAGJS9lMXRZ0i/QuickFit.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; float: right; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em 1.5em; max-width: none;\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">华硕独家秘笈 QuickFit虚拟尺标功能给用户带来更方便的编辑排版体验和解决方案。QuickFit 可以在您当前编辑处理的对象上提供和真实的照片或印刷物尺寸一样大小的模拟出版效果，节省打印样张的时间和减少纸张等耗材浪费，既环保又省钱。&nbsp;<br />\r\n支持的格式:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px 25px;\">\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">文件: 信件</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">图片: 8&rdquo;x10&rdquo;, 5&rdquo;x7&rdquo;, 4&rdquo;x6&rdquo;, 3&rdquo;x5&rdquo;, 2&rdquo;x2&rdquo;</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">网格: 对齐</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<div class=\"column first\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">风格独特且易于使用的设计，增添现代化的质感!</h4>\r\n<ul class=\"blackcircle\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none outside none;\">\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 13px; background-image: url(http://www.asus.com.cn/images/blackcircle.gif); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 5px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">多语言版本OSD设置菜单，提供多个控制快捷键。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 13px; background-image: url(http://www.asus.com.cn/images/blackcircle.gif); background-attachment: scroll; background-position