zelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\"><strong>精美优雅设计</strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">无与伦比的美丽</h3>\r\n<img class=\"right top\" alt=\"BEAUTY BEYOND BOUNDARIES\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/hj4Bczgud2bYy51f/mx02.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; float: right; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em 1.5em; max-width: none;\" />\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">华硕Designo MX系列显示器采用极具魅力的超薄机身，散发美丽的外观让您赏心悦目&mdash;MX279H最薄处仅为17.5mm&ndash;可将占用的空间降至最低。MX系列配备高品质时尚的无边框显示屏，边框仅为0.8mm。超薄整体日晷式底座彰显精美优雅设计，更能让您的显示器与任何台式电脑一起相得益彰。此外，MX系列设计荣获日本Good Design Award设计大奖。</p>\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center up_1\" alt=\"Subtle &amp; elegant design\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/hj4Bczgud2bYy51f/mx03.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-top: -20px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center up_1\" alt=\"Subtle &amp; elegant design\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/hj4Bczgud2bYy51f/mx04.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-top: -20px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\"><strong>栩栩如生、令人惊艳的视觉享受</strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">最新IPS技术及178&deg; 超广视角</h3>\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img alt=\"Vivid, lifelike visuals \" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/hj4Bczgud2bYy51f/mx05.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<p class=\"down_2\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 4em;\">Designo MX279H采用16:9 LED背光AH-IPS A+面板及178&deg; 超广视角，以确保从最极端的角度观赏，将色彩偏移降至最小化。AH-IPS是最新的IPS技术 &ndash; 提供精准色彩且绿色能效。</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\"><img class=\"left top\" alt=\"Vivid, lifelike visuals \" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/hj4Bczgud2bYy51f/arrowBlue.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; float: left; margin: 0px 1.5em 1.5em 0px; max-width: none; padding-bottom: 30px;\" />MX279H提供一个178&deg;(水平) / 178&deg;(垂直) 的超广可视角、高清AH-IPS A+面板，确保从最极端的角度观赏，屏幕上都能拥有最小化的色彩偏移。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">精美细节只为最佳用户体验</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">华硕Trace Free无残影技术藉由驱动液晶控制电压位准，以获得5ms (GTG)极速响应时间，消除视频播放时的拖影和残影，因而确保了影像清晰、流畅的播放效果。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center\" alt=\"Built tough and gamer-centric comfortable\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/hj4Bczgud2bYy51f/mx06.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\"><strong>华硕独家创新设计</strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">华硕智能动态对比度提供栩栩如生的视觉效果</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">采用 80,000,000:1 华硕智能对比度(ASCR)以及250cd/m&sup2;的亮度显示，藉由背光的亮度调整，令黑色更加深邃动人，亮色更加鲜明亮丽，细节表现更出众，画面内容更生动。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center\" alt=\"ASUS Smart Contrast Ratio for lifelike visuals \" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/hj4Bczgud2bYy51f/contrastRatio.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"columns_abbb\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">QuickFit 虚拟尺标提供您真正所见即所得的效果</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">MX279H配备华硕独家的 QuickFit虚拟尺标功能，允许用户在屏幕上预览相片及文件打印前的实际尺寸。它可通过显示器上的热键启动，提供非常有用的指南，仔细地以原尺寸浏览及编辑相片。</p>\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 218.296875px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<ul class=\"blackcircle\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none outside none;\"><strong>支持的格式:</strong>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 13px; background-image: url(http://www.asus.com.cn/images/blackcircle.gif); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 5px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">文件: A4, 信件格式</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 13px; background-image: url(http://www.asus.com.cn/images/blackcircle.gif); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 5px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">相片: 8&rdquo;x10&rdquo;, 5&rdquo;x7&rdquo;, 4&rdquo;x6&rdquo;, 3&rdquo;x5&rdquo;, 2&rdquo;x2&rdquo;</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 13px; background-image: url(http://www.asus.com.cn/images/blackcircle.gif); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 5px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">网格: 对齐</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 703.421875px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center up_1\" alt=\"QuickFit Virtual Scale\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/hj4Bczgud2bYy51f/vitualScalet.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-top: -20px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\"><strong>强劲的音频效果带来逼真的娱乐体验</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">Designo MX279H采用华硕金耳朵团队与 Bang&amp;Olufsen ICEpower&reg; 共同开发的华硕 SonicMaster技术。华硕独家音效技术通过硬件和软件优化，清晰的还原每个乐器的原声音效，为您带来身临其境般的立体声环绕效果，享受更响亮，更细微的清透音质和巅峰音效。</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">更大的扬声器提供更广更流畅的输出</h3>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">对于采用超薄设计的MX279H而言，增加强劲的音效系统是一项艰巨的挑战。然而，MX279H采用32mm大直径扬声器，提供强劲的音频效果及优异的低音性能。同时，提供100cc的音盆，可让华硕MX279H显示器具有强劲的音频功能。</p>\r\n内置放大器专为扬声器声音的再现提供动力，就像一辆汽车的发动机一样，拥有强劲的马力可以达到出色的性能。MX279H的每个声道使用高达5W放大器，扬声器包含大量的稀土磁体产生更强大的震撼音效。</div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center\" alt=\"Premium Immersive Audio\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/hj4Bczgud2bYy51f/mx07.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">Bang &amp; Olufsen ICEpower&reg;提供强劲的音效</h3>\r\n<br />\r\n<img class=\"right top\" alt=\"Audio by Bang &amp; Olufsen ICEpower&reg;\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/hj4Bczgud2bYy51f/web-ALL_30.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; float: right; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em 1.5em; max-width: none;\" />\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">华硕MX279H 提供精确完美的图像及令人惊艳的影音性能，无论您是观赏电影，玩游戏或聆听音乐，它皆可提供全方位的多媒体体验。采用先进的Bang &amp; Olufsen ICEpower&reg;音效技术，在超薄机身内整合了强劲的音效系统，打造无与伦比的音频功能，从而不再需要台式电脑的外接喇叭。&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMX279H采用的Bang &amp; Olufsen ICEpower&reg; 技术专为简约媒体产品而精心设计，不仅节省空间，而且提供强劲的音频效果。卓越的音频质量是华硕创新技术、充足的供电及音频工程师数月的优化与调校的成效。通常来说，强劲的音效就会意味着高能耗，但MX279H并非如此。此显示屏内嵌高效能的Class D MobileSound 3 技术，可将92 %的电源输入转换为有用音效输出。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\"><strong>高扩展性可连接更多多媒体设备</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">Designo MX279H支持全高清1920 x 1080分辨率，配备双HDMI高清接口及D-sub (VGA)输入接口，提供各种多媒体娱乐，简单的连接便能播放蓝光光碟以及操控游戏，打造全高清1080P的视觉盛宴。</p>\r\n<img class=\"center up_1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Audio by Bang &amp; Olufsen ICEpower&reg;\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/CN/products/hj4Bczgud2bYy51f/04.jpg\" longdesc=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/Monitors_Projectors/MX279H/\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-top: -20px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\"><strong>在您的台式电脑上彰显MX风格</strong></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">桌面壁纸下载</h3>\r\n<br />\r\n<table style=\"max-width: 100%; background-color: transparent; border-spacing: 0px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 20px; padding-right: 20px;\"><a href=\"http://event.asus.com/2012/LCD/MX_Series_wallpaper/a.zip\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-decoration: none;\"><img alt=\"Wallpaper\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/hj4Bczgud2bYy51f/mXwall_1.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 20px; padding-right: 20px;\"><a href=\"http://event.asus.com/2012/LCD/MX_Series_wallpaper/b.zip\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-decoration: none;\"><img alt=\"Wallpaper\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/hj4Bczgud2bYy51f/mXwall_2.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 20px; padding-right: 20px;\"><a href=\"http://event.asus.com/2012/LCD/MX_Series_wallpaper/c.zip\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-decoration: none;\"><img alt=\"Wallpaper\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/hj4Bczgud2bYy51f/mXwall_3.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></a></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><a href=\"http://event.asus.com/2012/LCD/MX_Series_wallpaper/d.zip\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-decoration: none;\"><img alt=\"Wallpaper\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/produc