ght: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center\" alt=\"Superior Image Quality Meets Frameless Elegant Design\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/vGonKXSmscttmtDh/vx03_2.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">丰富的接口，无限享受多媒体娱乐功能</h4>\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">VX279N-W采用丰富的连接性包括DVI-D接口和D-sub接口，让您无限享受多媒体娱乐功能。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center\" title=\"Extensive Connectivity\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/vGonKXSmscttmtDh/io_port.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 28px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">栩栩如生、令人惊艳的视觉享受</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">最新IPS技术及178&deg;超广视角</h3>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img alt=\"Vivid, lifelike visuals \" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/vGonKXSmscttmtDh/vx05.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<p class=\"down_3\" style=\"margin: 60px 0px 4em;\">VX279N-W采用16:9 LED背光AH-IPS A+面板及178&deg;超广视角，以确保从最极端的角度观赏，将色彩偏移降至最小化。AH-IPS是最新的IPS技术&ndash;提供精准色彩且绿色能效。</p>\r\n<img class=\"up_1\" alt=\"Vivid, lifelike visuals\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/vGonKXSmscttmtDh/ips_wide.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-top: -20px; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">80,000,000:1华硕智能动态对比度</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">采用 80,000,000:1 华硕智能对比度(ASCR)以及250cd/m&sup2;的亮度显示，藉由背光的亮度调整，令黑色更加深邃动人，亮色更加鲜明亮丽，细节表现更出众，画面内容更生动。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center\" alt=\"80,000,000:1 ASUS Smart Contrast Ratio\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/vGonKXSmscttmtDh/contrastRatio.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_ab\" style=\"width: 946px;\"><img class=\"top left\" alt=\"ASUS-exclusive VividPixel Technology\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/jRnfwIfotLRFPP1L/vividPixel.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; float: left; margin: 0px 1.5em 1.5em 0px; max-width: none;\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">华硕独家VividPixel技术</h3>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">VividPixel技术用来增强图像及视频的轮廓，锐度和色彩饱和度，提供高品质的视觉体验。</p>\r\n<br style=\"clear: both;\" />\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 460.859375px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\"><img alt=\"Monitor without VividPixel\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/vGonKXSmscttmtDh/pixel_1.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">显示器没有搭配VividPixel技术</h4>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px 25px;\">\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">图像质量主要依赖于面板本身</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">如果原始图像质量不好，则会产生模糊。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">通常人们没有注意到这个细节，因为没有进行比较。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 460.859375px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\"><img alt=\"Monitor without VividPixel\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/vGonKXSmscttmtDh/pixel_2.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: none;\" /></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">VX 系列- IPS面板搭配VividPixel技术</h4>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px 25px;\">\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">IPS面板带给您超凡视觉享受</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">VividPixel默认值为25，自动调校图像质量。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px;\">在VividPixel设置中选择其中的5个选项来浏览更多的不同效果。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.asus.com/Display/Features/Splendid_Technology/\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-decoration: none;\"><img class=\"right top down_2\" title=\"Learn More on Splendid Technology\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/images/icons/LCD/splendid_with_srgb.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em 1.5em; float: right; max-width: none;\" /></a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">Splendid&trade;靓彩影像增强技术</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">智能靓彩技术通过对亮度、对比度、色彩的锐利度、饱和度以及色温、肤色色度等智能处理和调节，还可以通过热键来切换6种不同的情景模式（风景、剧院、游戏、夜间、sRGB和标准模式），使得色彩和图像质量表现的更完美和生动。</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"columns_abbb\" style=\"width: 946px;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px;\">华硕独家QuickFit虚拟比例</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em;\">VX279N-W配备华硕独家QuickFit虚拟比例功能，允许用户在屏幕上预览相片及文件打印前的实际尺寸。它可通过显示器上的热键启动，并以此为指南精准地预览及编辑照片。</p>\r\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: left; width: 218.296875px; margin-left: 0px;\">\r\n<ul class=\"blackcircle\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none outside none;\"><strong>支持格式:</strong>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 13px; background-image: url(http://www.asus.com.cn/images/blackcircle.gif); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 5px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">文件：A4, 信件</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 13px; background-image: url(http://www.asus.com.cn/images/blackcircle.gif); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 5px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">图片：8&rdquo;x10&rdquo;, 5&rdquo;x7&rdquo;, 4&rdquo;x6&rdquo;, 3&rdquo;x5&rdquo;, 2&rdquo;x2&rdquo;</li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 13px; background-image: url(http://www.asus.com.cn/images/blackcircle.gif); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 5px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">坐标预览：实际尺寸、厘米与英寸</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column last\" style=\"padding: 0px; float: right; width: 703.421875px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><img class=\"center up_1\" alt=\"QuickFit Virtual Scale\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/vGonKXSmscttmtDh/vitualScalet.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; margin-top: -20px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block; max-width: none;\" /></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>