 世界。藉由新技术，能够呈现出最高双倍亮度的图像以及远比同类技术丰富的色彩，从而可大幅提升 3D 体验。目前已有数百款热门 PC 游戏**兼容于 NVIDIA&reg; 3D Vision&trade;套件。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">* 请访问<a href=\"http://www.nvidia.com/object/3D_Vision_3D_Games.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-decoration: none;\">NVIDIA web site</a>了解更多信息.</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important;\">通过NVIDIA&reg; 3D LightBoost&trade; 技术让您沉浸在超流畅且生动的 3D 动感世界</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px;\"><img class=\"right top\" title=\"NVIDIA&reg; 3D LightBoost&trade; Technology\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/scyOAkYbYqeWhq8e/3D_LightBoost.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; float: right; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em 1.5em; max-width: none;\" />藉由最新的NVIDIA&reg; 3D LightBoost&trade; 技术，享受双倍于普通3D技术的亮度且不会增加能耗。非常适合于黑色游戏，如Metro 2033和Batman: Arkham City. 另外，捆绑NVIDIA&reg; 3D LightBoost&trade; 技术的新一代眼镜专为游戏玩家以及 3D 发烧友而设计，具有诸多全新特性，通过将镜片增大20%，实现更宽的视野以及更好的光线遮挡效果，佩戴更加舒适，让在游戏中能够提供超越第一代眼镜的临场感。</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 21px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important;\">极致流畅的运动影像</h3>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important;\">144Hz双倍刷新率及2ms响应时间</h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px;\"><img class=\"right top\" title=\"2ms Response Time\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/scyOAkYbYqeWhq8e/2ms.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; float: right; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em 1.5em; max-width: none;\" /><img class=\"right top\" title=\"120Hz Double-speed Refresh Rate\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/scyOAkYbYqeWhq8e/120Hz_RefreshRate.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; float: right; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em 1.5em; max-width: none;\" />Trace Free II 二代无拖影技术带来史无前例的流畅视频体验。144Hz的超高刷新率提供双倍于其他显示器的扫描性能,在剧情紧张的动作电影中带来史无前例的顺畅体验。响应时间缩短到2ms,通过精确控制加在液晶体单位的驱动电压实现消除拖影和带来清楚流畅的视频回放效果。</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0.4em; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 18px; background-image: none; height: auto; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important;\">先进的双边驱动技术</h4>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px;\">双边LCD驱动技术使3D影像更清晰流畅。与传统的单边驱动LCD显示器相比，VG278H能有效的缩短响应时间，有效防止画面拖影 、残影、过分曝光的发生，带来更加清晰流畅的3D游戏和电影体验。</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.asus.com/FeatureList.aspx?PG_ID=6DXFKkHS5lvEb99r&amp;F_ID=44\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 185, 255); text-decoration: none; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px;\"><img class=\"right top\" title=\"Splendid&trade; Video Intelligence Technology\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" alt=\"Learn More on Splendid Technology\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/images/icons/LCD/splendid_with_srgb_black.jpg\" style=\"height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; float: right; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em 1.5em; max-width: none;\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0p